{"type": "article", "id": 8151, "title": "Rick Owens & Adidas 鞋履", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-07T08:01:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052348549GbLCkvYBPzU0Rma.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"white-space:normal;\">Rick Owens 和 Adidas </span>这几年合作频频，且作品颇受好评。继去年推出银色 Springblade Boost 后，最近又推出了黑色和白色两款纯色的设计，鞋身采用全皮革材质，鞋头采用麂皮材质，小细节彰显品质。最酷的是Rick Owens 标志性的鞋底，狂野大方而充满未来感。鞋子目前售价 765 美元，<a href=\"https://www.ssense.com/en-us/men/product/rick-owens/white-adidas-by-rick-owens-springblade-boots/577503\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234852glkSqebwXDdyGh9L.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052348523GzOkI6x7Ag4yfYd.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.03359684\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234853Vh4eqBAwUPp9gXY0.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.86944444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234853QtCX9JF2LYiUZ5gy.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.00927644\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}